properties.name: Johnson House
properties.desc: The Johnson House is a safehouse on Grove Street in Ganton, Los Santos in Grand Theft Auto: San Andreas.

properties.name: Safehouse
properties.desc: These safe houses are purchasable properties containing a save icon as well as a wardrobe, which distinguishes them from save points. Safe houses may also contain usable garages, capable of storing up to four vehicles.
